# Build context ignore rules for docker/Dockerfile.chip-test ONLY.
#
# BuildKit automatically uses this file instead of the repo-root .dockerignore
# when the build targets this Dockerfile (`-f docker/Dockerfile.chip-test`).
# It fully replaces the root .dockerignore (no merge).
#
# This image clones Matterbridge, the plugins and connectedhomeip from GitHub and
# builds them; it uses no local source. From the context it copies only the
# docker/chip-test/ fixtures and docker/entrypoint.chip-test.sh, so we ignore
# everything else.

# Ignore everything...
*

# ...except the files this Dockerfile copies.
!docker/chip-test
!docker/entrypoint.chip-test.sh
